{"tid":2413821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大集團疫市死頂開超市｜建華連開6間滲透中產市場 富臨 扒王 龍豐開超市散貨","createTime":"2021-02-19T03:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T04:10:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5ede6c2f96e4fb87d5cfe32f7a7ac5fa6edf5a11","tid":2413821,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"疫情重擊零售餐飲業，人人在家抗疫煮飯，本身生意難撈﹐不少來貨賣不出去，不如另開超市散貨。本刊發現近日，不少地方都新開超市，原來大部分皆出自大集團之手，當中堪稱「街市霸主」的建華集團亦分一杯羹，由賣豬肉到橫跨鮮肉、凍肉、蔬果等板塊，去年更逆市連開6間超市，成立新品牌「本灣水產」和「FRESH 新鮮生活」，分別座落民生區和私人大型屋苑。<br />\n<br />\n不止建華、包括連鎖餐飲集團富臨及扒王之王賣自家凍肉；「藥房大王」龍豐轉型搞超市售水貨；發展商九建與恒發則紛紛於自家物業開超市，用盡租不出的地方。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_776573_0/%E5%A4%A7%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E7%96%AB%E5%B8%82%E6%AD%BB%E9%A0%82%E9%96%8B%E8%B6%85%E5%B8%82-%E5%BB%BA%E8%8F%AF%E9%80%A3%E9%96%8B6%E9%96%93%E6%BB%B2%E9%80%8F%E4%B8%AD%E7%94%A2%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E5%AF%8C%E8%87%A8-%E6%89%92%E7%8E%8B-%E9%BE%8D%E8%B1%90%E9%96%8B%E8%B6%85%E5%B8%82%E6%95%A3%E8%B2%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_776573_0%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%259C%2598%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%25A0%2582%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25B6%2585%25E5%25B8%2582-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%258F%25AF%25E9%2580%25A3%25E9%2596%258B6%25E9%2596%2593%25E6%25BB%25B2%25E9%2580%258F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E5%25AF%258C%25E8%2587%25A8-%25E6%2589%2592%25E7%258E%258B-%25E9%25BE%258D%25E8%25B1%2590%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25B6%2585%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%2595%25A3%25E8%25B2%25A8&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69IleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=dc09d150\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_776573_0%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%259C%2598%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%25A0%2582%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25B6%2585%25E5%25B8%2582-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%258F%25AF%25E9%2580%25A3%25E9%2596%258B6%25E9%2596%2593%25E6%25BB%25B2%25E9%2580%258